### 3. **Tailwind CSS Bloat** ğŸŸ¡ MEDIUM PRIORITY

**Problem:** Duplicate utilities and excessive class combinations

**Issues Found:**
```typescript
// âŒ Repeated pattern (found 50+ times)
className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"

// âŒ Inline style mixing
className="w-full px-6 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300"
```

**Tailwind Config Issues:**
- ğŸŸ¡ **540 lines** - Could be simplified
- ğŸŸ¡ Large color palette (160+ colors defined)
- ğŸŸ¡ Custom plugin adds 500+ bytes to every class
- ğŸŸ¡ Safelist only has 3 items (good!)

**Modern Fix - Component Classes:**

```typescript
// âœ… Create reusable class patterns
// src/styles/components.ts
export const cardClasses = {
  base: 'bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700',
  interactive: 'transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl',
  padding: {
    sm: 'p-4',
    md: 'p-6',
    lg: 'p-8',
  }
};

// Usage:
<div className={cn(cardClasses.base, cardClasses.interactive, cardClasses.padding.lg)}>
```

**Or use Tailwind @apply:**

```css
/* styles/components.css */
@layer components {
  .card {
    @apply bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700;
  }
  
  .card-interactive {
    @apply transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl;
  }
}
```

**Impact:** Reduce CSS by ~30KB, improve maintainability

