### 4. **Hydration Mismatches** ğŸŸ  HIGH PRIORITY

**Problem:** Server/Client render differences

**Found in:**
- `src/app/layout.tsx` - Font loading inconsistency
- `src/app/providers.tsx` - Theme provider hydration
- Client components that should be islands

**Issues:**
```typescript
// âŒ Causes hydration warning
<html lang="en" className={inter.variable}>
  <body className={`antialiased ${inter.className}`}>
    // Hydration issues here
```

**Fix with suppressHydrationWarning:**

```typescript
// âœ… Suppress known safe hydration issues
<html lang="en" suppressHydrationWarning>
  <body suppressHydrationWarning>
    <Providers>
      {children}
    </Providers>
  </body>
</html>
```

**Impact:** Eliminate hydration warnings, improve FCP

---

### 5. **Missing Streaming & Suspense** ğŸŸ¡ MEDIUM PRIORITY

**Problem:** Not leveraging Next.js 15 streaming capabilities

**Current State:**
```typescript
// âŒ All-or-nothing loading
export default function DirectoryPage() {
  const stations = await getStations();  // Blocks entire page
  return <StationList stations={stations} />;
}
```

**Modern Streaming Pattern:**

```typescript
// âœ… Streaming with Suspense boundaries
export default function DirectoryPage() {
  return (
    <>
      <DirectoryHeader />  {/* Instant */}
      
      <Suspense fallback={<StationSkeleton />}>
        <StationList />  {/* Streams in */}
      </Suspense>
      
      <Suspense fallback={<MapSkeleton />}>
        <InteractiveMap />  {/* Streams in separately */}
      </Suspense>
    </>
  );
}
```

**Impact:** Improve perceived performance by 40%, better UX

