### 6. **Layout Shift Issues (CLS)** ğŸŸ¡ MEDIUM PRIORITY

**Problem:** Missing dimensions on dynamic content

**Found:**
- Images without explicit width/height
- Skeletons don't match final content size
- Map containers change size on load

**Fix:**

```typescript
// âŒ Causes CLS
<Image src="/hero.jpg" fill alt="Hero" />

// âœ… Prevents CLS
<Image 
  src="/hero.jpg" 
  width={1200} 
  height={630}
  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px"
  alt="Hero"
/>

// âœ… Reserve space for dynamic content
<div className="h-[600px] w-full">  {/* Fixed height */}
  <InteractiveMap />
</div>
```

**Impact:** Improve CLS score from 0.15 to < 0.1

