## ğŸ¯ MODERN FIXES & OPTIMIZATIONS

### Fix #1: Lazy Load Framer Motion (HIGH PRIORITY)

**Create:** `src/components/motion/LazyMotion.tsx`

```typescript
'use client';

import { LazyMotion, domAnimation, m } from 'framer-motion';
import { ReactNode } from 'react';

/**
 * Lazy-loaded motion wrapper
 * Reduces bundle size by ~40KB by loading only features you use
 */
export function MotionProvider({ children }: { children: ReactNode }) {
  return (
    <LazyMotion features={domAnimation} strict>
      {children}
    </LazyMotion>
  );
}

// Export optimized motion components
export { m as motion };
```

**Usage:**

```typescript
// âŒ BEFORE - Imports entire library
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';

// âœ… AFTER - Only loads what you need
import { motion, MotionProvider } from '@/components/motion/LazyMotion';

<MotionProvider>
  <motion.div />
</MotionProvider>
```

**Impact:** 40KB reduction per page

